* The Button texts are not internationalized and can't be set from the
  application.

* There needs to be a way to set the DISPLAY via the assuan interface.

* There needs to be a way to set the terminal node and type ($TERM
  value) at the command line and via the assuan interface.

* The KDE and curses PIN entry need enhanced mode.

* The KDE PIN entry needs to use libpinentry (maybe).

* Configure checks for KDE libs and features are needed.
